cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.AI, cs.CR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper focuses on Spoken Language Understanding and Natural Language Understanding, which are subfields of NLP (Natural Language Processing) that fall under cs.CL. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses the machine learning architecture of the Snips Voice Platform, which involves training high-performance machine learning models. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering): The paper presents a software solution for performing Spoken Language Understanding on microprocessors typical of IoT devices. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the use of machine learning for Spoken Language Understanding and Natural Language Understanding, which are subfields of AI. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): The paper emphasizes privacy by design, as no personal user data is ever collected, which falls under the domain of security and privacy in computer science.
